		<category name="Jakobs Clockwork Rifles">
			<comment>Made by Coleby</comment>
			<comment>Makes Jakobs ARs fire automatically with slow fire rate and decent accuracy loss</comment>
			<category name="Dumb Magic">
				<code profiles="default">set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.A_Weapons.WT_Jakobs_AssaultRifle AutomaticBurstCount 0</code>
				<code profiles="default">set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.A_Weapons.WT_Jakobs_AssaultRifle PerShotAccuracyImpulse 1</code>
				<code profiles="default">set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.A_Weapons.WT_Jakobs_AssaultRifle FireRate 0.185</code>
				<code profiles="default">set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.A_Weapons.WT_Jakobs_AssaultRifle:AttributePresentationDefinition_3 NoConstraintText Uses a [shock]clockwork mechanism[-shock] to fire slow, but automatically.</code>
			</category>
